# Tech Stack

- **Pattern**: BFF (Backend for Frontend) â€” the browser talks only to the app's backend; the backend talks to external services.
- **Framework**: Svelte 5 (Runes API only: $state, $derived, $effect, $props)
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: PandaCSS + Iconify
- **Database**: Neon (Postgres) + Drizzle ORM
- **Authentication**: Auth0 (BFF-managed sessions, **custom in-app login page**, no Universal Login)
- **File Storage**: Vercel Blob
- **Real-time / RPC**: tRPC v11 (HTTP for queries/mutations, WebSocket for subscriptions)
- **Pub/Sub Infrastructure**: Redis (Upstash Redis or compatible cluster)
- **Deployment**: Vercel
- **Tooling**: Biome (unified linter/formatter/import sorter)